pib - Python Image Browser
--------------------------
                                (c) 2010 Philip Kranz
                                http://github.com/talanis85/pib

A keyboard-oriented image viewer/browser written in Python/Tk.


Features:
    - Completely keyboard-based navigation
    - Asynchronous preloading of images

Todo:
    - Preview of directories
    - Pretty interface (probably impossible with Tk)
    - Better performance

